==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|/sĕnt/}}
*{{IPA|/sent/}}
*{{SAMPA|/sEnt/}}

====Homophones====
*[[cent]]
*[[sent]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# an [[odour]] or [[smell]], especially one left by an animal being [[hunt]]ed by [[hound]]s.
# something with a strong odour.
#:''the scent of [[flower]]s''
#:''the scent of a [[skunk]]''
# [[perfume]].
# (''Figurative'') any [[trail]] or [[trace]] that can be followed to find something or someone.

====Synonyms====
*[[fragrance]]
*[[perfume]]

